{
  "stem": "19921.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 151.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- some of them were prosecuted, you know, [INAUDIBLE] thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Eventually, they were released.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody got shot except in hand-to-hand fighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But whoever they thought did wrong got the lessons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whatever they did with them-- five years or two years or whatever-- I had nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we had to clear the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was-- so that was the role of the army in Poland--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's after the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wouldn't do anything if they wouldn't bother anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they shot people, unfortunately, people which came from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the people which they shot there was a rabbi's son, which was very, very involved in the uprising, I found out later-- in the uprising of Sobibor in 1942.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and he was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was [INAUDIBLE]-- he was killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just-- one of them got just married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were five, five men and one girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all wiped out, just like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too much, not too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think about not more than six weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was involved with one of those big raids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the end for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the end for me, because I put in for the-- for the retirement from my army duty.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that was the point-- that's right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would have to stay for another three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know my friends did it, for-- stayed for another two years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
